Question: There are six or more vending machines that have food or drinks.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/736x/cc/f0/bf/ccf0bf89249d55185c6f581d2a6442f2--vending-machines-i-want-to.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many vending machines are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many vending machines are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} >= 6 or {ANSWER1} >= 6')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
